<div class="mx-auto md:w-2/3 w-full">
<h1 class="font-bold text-4xl mb-6">Adjust the number of heats</h1>

<p class="mb-2">
You can indirectly control the number of heats by adjusting who can be
on the floor at the same time.
</p>

<p class="mb-2">
With the sliders all the way to the left, Open and Closed heats are never
on the floor at the same time, Full Bronze students can only be on the floor
with other Full Bronze students.  And people in age category B1 can only
be on the floor with others in the same age category.
</p>

<p class="mb-2">
With the sliders all the way to the right, Open and Closed heats can be 
on the floor at the same time, Newcomers can be on the dance floor at the
same time as Full Gold students.  And people in any age category can be
on the floor at the same time.
</p>

<%= form_with url: redo_heats_path, local: true, data: {turbo: false} do |form| %>
  <div class="my-5">
    <%= form.label :category, 'open/closed' %>
    <%= form.range_field :category, min: 0, max: 1, value: 0, class: "block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-200 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" %>
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <%= form.label :level, 'level' %>
    <%= form.range_field :level, min: 0, max: @levels, value: @levels/2, class: "block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-200 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" %>
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <%= form.label :age, 'age' %>
    <%= form.range_field :age, min: 0, max: @categories, value: @categories, class: "block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-200 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" %>
  </div>

  <div class="inline">
    <%= form.submit value: 'Redo', class: "rounded-lg py-3 px-5 bg-blue-600 text-white inline-block font-medium cursor-pointer" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
</div>
